	DS3231 RTC Module Selection
The project required accurate real-time scheduling functionality for automation tasks including automatic light activation, automatic device shutdown and reminder notifications. Several RTC hardware modules were evaluated during system design to identify the most suitable solution for reliable automation scheduling..
 
Figure 3.5 DS3231 Real-Time Clock Module Used for Automation Scheduling

RTC Module	Advantages	Limitations	Reason for Final Selection
DS1307 RTC	Low cost, simple implementation, widely available	Lower accuracy, affected by temperature changes, requires external crystal stability	Not selected due to lower timekeeping accuracy and weaker long-term reliability
